ListInfo.Name: Profile - Software Developer
ListInfo.Description: This list details the essential traits and qualifications that are typically required or desirable for a Software Developer role. It acts as a foundational guide for candidate evaluation during the hiring process.
ListInfo.Instructions: Reference this list when posting job ads, conducting interviews, and evaluating candidates to ensure a comprehensive understanding of the qualifications needed for a software developer.

ListItem.Value: Proficiency in at least one programming language such as Java, C++, Python, or JavaScript.
Strong understanding of the software development lifecycle and methodologies (Agile, Scrum, Kanban).
